data.description: Welcome home to this great 4 bedroom 2.5 bathroom home located in Taylors. The front porch is a great place to enjoy your morning coffee. Entering the home you are greeted with a living room to the left that opens into the dining room. The open kitchen overlooks the family room with a cozy gas log fireplace. Located upstairs are your four bedrooms, including the master with a spacious closet, jetted tub, dual sinks, and separate shower. Relax in your fenced in backyard with plenty of space for fun activities. You will be a short drive to many of your favorite restaurants and shopping on Wade Hampton, a 15 minute drive to downtown Greenville, and a 10 minute drive to downtown Greer. Don't miss out on your chance to make this home yours!
